23#pragma once
24
25#include "CachedResource.h"
26#include "SVGDocument.h"
27#include "TextResourceDecoder.h"
28
29namespace WebCore {
30
31class Settings;
32
33class CachedSVGDocument final : public CachedResource {
34public:
35 explicit CachedSVGDocument(CachedResourceRequest&&, PAL::SessionID, const CookieJar*, const Settings&);
36 explicit CachedSVGDocument(CachedResourceRequest&&, CachedSVGDocument&);
37 virtual ~CachedSVGDocument();
38
39 SVGDocument* document() const { return m_document.get(); }
40
41private:
42 bool mayTryReplaceEncodedData() const override { return true; }
43 void setEncoding(const String&) override;
44 String encoding() const override;
45 const TextResourceDecoder* textResourceDecoder() const override { return m_decoder.get(); }
46 void finishLoading(SharedBuffer*, const NetworkLoadMetrics&) override;
47
48 RefPtr<SVGDocument> m_document;
49 RefPtr<TextResourceDecoder> m_decoder;
50 const Ref<const Settings> m_settings;
51};
52
53} // namespace WebCore
54
55SPECIALIZE_TYPE_TRAITS_CACHED_RESOURCE(CachedSVGDocument, CachedResource::Type::SVGDocumentResource)
